{
  "chapter": 19,
  "chapter_summary": "清晨，西门吹雪在花旁静立，宫九的马车到来。西门吹雪拔剑刺马，阻止宫九追赶陆小凤。宫九被西门吹雪的杀气震慑，不敢妄动。陆小凤安全脱身后想起西门吹雪的安危，折返回来。在西门吹雪住处，陆小凤发现地上的血迹，以为西门吹雪遭了不测。西门吹雪安然现身，两人重逢。西门吹雪讲述了与宫九对峙的经过：宫九有自虐癖好，哀求西门吹雪打他，甚至让牛肉汤鞭打自己，西门吹雪看得呕吐不止。两人讨论房子的价值，西门吹雪决定搬走，让陆小凤藏身于此，自己去找老实和尚学坐怀不乱，顺便接沙曼和小玉来。陆小凤则希望找到杀死宫九的方法。鹰眼老七奉宫九之命带二十名黑衣人暗算西门吹雪，陆小凤偷听到他们的谈话，决定出手阻止。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你为什么要杀我的马？”",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "“我不希望你的马追上我的朋友。”",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“假如我要追呢？”",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "“你的人，就会和你的马一样下场。”",
      "tone": "威胁",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你有自信吗？”",
      "tone": "冷哼",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "“西门吹雪是江湖上最有自信的人。”",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“真的吗？”",
      "tone": "质疑",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "“你要不要试一试？”",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“你在凭吊那匹马？”",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“这不是你的血？”",
      "tone": "关切",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“是的话，我还会站在这里吗？”",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“哦，对，这是马的血。”",
      "tone": "恍然",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“你为什么要赶回来？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“我害怕。”",
      "tone": "坦诚",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“你害怕我会遭宫九的毒手？”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“就凭你这点，你以后来找我办事，我不要你剃胡子了。”",
      "tone": "感动",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你确实让我担上了心。”",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“你以为我会死？”",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“是的。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“为什么？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“因为你是个极爱清洁的人，岂能容许一滩血在你屋前？”",
      "tone": "推理",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“我当然不能容忍，只是我没有时间去清洗。”",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你没有时间？”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“是的，我还未来得及清洗，你就来了。”",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“我来以前呢？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“我正在河边吐。”",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“吐？呕吐？”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你为什么要吐？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“因为我见到一个人，他的举动丑陋得令我非吐不可。”",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“谁？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“宫九。”",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“宫九？他怎么啦？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“他哀求我打他。”",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你打了吗？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“没有。高手过招前的凝视，绝不能疏忽，我以为他是故意扰乱我的注意力。”",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“然后呢？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“然后他忽然举起手来，自己打自己的脸。”",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你还是没有理他？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“你说对了。我依旧目不转睛地看着他。”",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“他怎么办？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“他挨了鞭子。”",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“挨谁的鞭子？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“牛肉汤的。牛肉汤不停的打他，他在地上翻滚，高兴得大叫。”",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你怎么办？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“我赶快冲到河边，大吐特吐，要不然……”",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“要不然就怎样？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“要不然我吐在地上，这里我就不能再住了。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“那恐怕我就要赔你一栋房子了。”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“你知道我这栋房子价值多少吗？”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“值多少？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“你知道霍休吗？”",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你要把你的房子和霍老头的相提并论？”",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“你猜错了。”",
      "tone": "否定",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“我猜错了？”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“我只不过是说，任何一栋房子，都是无价的。”",
      "tone": "哲理",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“为什么？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“因为房子里的人，也许有一天也会名动四方的。”",
      "tone": "深意",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你说得一点也不错，霍老头的那栋木屋，在陆放翁行吟的时候，根本也只不过是一堆木头盖起来的房子而已，但是陆放翁的诗受到世人的赏识以后，到了霍老头住的时候，就价值连城了。”",
      "tone": "赞同",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“所以假如我不能住在这里，这种房子你也赔不起。”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你错了，我赔得起。”",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“哦？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“因为我现在根本不必赔给你，等几百年后，后世的人都还知道有个西门吹雪的时候，我已经羽化登仙去了。”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“我发现你会耍赖。”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“就算是吧，也赖不到你身上，因为你现在根本不会搬走。”",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“这次是你错了。”",
      "tone": "否定",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“哦？”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“我马上就要搬走。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“为什么？”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“因为，这里适合你住。”",
      "tone": "关切",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“适合我住？”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“宫九一定以为你已经走了，怎么也想不到你还会回来，所以他不管派出多少耳目，不管他的耳目在哪里探听，都再也打听不到你的行踪。”",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“因为我已经在你这里高枕无忧了。”",
      "tone": "轻松",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“完全正确。”",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“那么你呢？”",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“我走。”",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你去哪里？”",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“我去学佛。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“学佛？跟谁？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“当然跟和尚。”",
      "tone": "理所当然",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“跟哪一位和尚？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“老实和尚！”",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“老实和尚懂佛？”",
      "tone": "怀疑",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“我不知道。”",
      "tone": "坦诚",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你不知道？你不知道还要跟他学？”",
      "tone": "不解",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“我只跟他学一招。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“哪一招？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“坐怀不乱。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“坐怀不乱？学来干什么？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“学来对着两个大美人的时候，不会心猿意马。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“两个大美人又是谁？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“一个叫沙曼，一个叫小玉。”",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“你是说，你要去接他们来这里？”",
      "tone": "惊喜",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“你有比这更安全更好的方法吗？”",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“有。”",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“请说。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“只是我们暂时都做不到。”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "“那是什么方法？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "“杀死宫九的方法。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“十二连环坞鹰眼老七求见西门公子。”",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人甲",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "text": "“咱哥儿俩今天晚上去翻翻本，然后再去找春红和桃娘乐上一乐如何？”",
      "tone": "轻佻",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人乙",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "text": "“翻你个大头鬼！”",
      "tone": "烦躁",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人甲",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "text": "“你怎么啦！”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人乙",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "text": "“你知道我生平最怕的一件事是什么吗？”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人甲",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "text": "“是什么？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人乙",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "text": "“就是摸门钉。有一次我去办事，也是找不到人，结果我去推了几把牌九，哈，你知道结果吗？连续二十七把，我拿的都是炮十。”",
      "tone": "抱怨",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人甲",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "text": "“所以你今天没看到西门吹雪，你就不赌？”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人乙",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "text": "“绝不赌。”",
      "tone": "坚决",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人甲",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "text": "“我劝你还是痛痛快快赌一场的好。”",
      "tone": "劝告",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人乙",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "text": "“为什么？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人甲",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "text": "“因为你见到西门吹雪，恐怕就不一定有机会赌了。”",
      "tone": "警告",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人乙",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "text": "“你是说我们杀不了他？”",
      "tone": "不服",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人甲",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "text": "“我只怕是没有可能。”",
      "tone": "悲观",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人乙",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "text": "“不可能。”",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人甲",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "text": "“你那么自信？”",
      "tone": "质疑",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren_2",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人乙",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren_1",
      "text": "“当然，我们二十个人在他全无提防之下，忽然发了二十种不同的暗器，我看神仙恐怕也难躲得过，何况只不过是凡人而已。”",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 19
    }
